# Netlify SPA redirects
# This ensures all routes redirect to index.html for client-side routing

/*    /index.html   200

# Optional: Redirect www to non-www (uncomment if needed)
# https://www.your-domain.com/* https://your-domain.com/:splat 301!

# Optional: Force HTTPS (uncomment if needed)
# http://your-domain.com/* https://your-domain.com/:splat 301!
# http://www.your-domain.com/* https://your-domain.com/:splat 301!